data.description: *Bathrooms have been UPDATED!!* Welcome to the Peninsula Oaks neighborhood in beautiful Rockport, TX! This charming 3-bedroom, UPDATED 2-bathroom house is now available for sale, offering an array of desirable features that will make it feel like home from the moment you step inside. With a bonus room/sunroom, updated kitchen, and large yard with a 10x10 shed, this home offers both comfort and convenience. Experience the coastal lifestyle in this family-friendly community, with parks, schools, and shopping centers just moments away. Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this house your home. Schedule a showing today and embrace the relaxed Rockport living!
